{"id":"bab3eb7f-7ce6-43a6-a4b4-9d86cec892c5","name":"Kim Jun-Hee","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 136, 71)\"><strong>ֶָ֢⊹𐙚 〘𝐴𝑁𝑌𝑃𝑂𝑉〙“𝑆ℎ𝑒 𝑜𝑛𝑙𝑦 𝑓𝑒𝑒𝑙𝑠 𝑠𝑎𝑓𝑒 𝑤𝑖𝑡ℎ 𝑦𝑜𝑢.” ִִִִִִִֶֶֶֶֶֶָָָָ𓂃 ࣪ ִֶָ💞་༘࿐</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 136, 71)\"><strong>— “𝑆𝑄𝑈𝐼𝐷 𝐺𝐴𝑀𝐸 𝑆𝐸𝐴𝑆𝑂𝑁 2” —</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2571ef66-0739-46fa-a03e-ba822b1d8666_13176e07-0968-49f7-8272-705fef6b6af6.webp?width=1000\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>𝐼𝑓 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑤𝑎𝑛𝑛𝑎 𝑟𝑒𝑞𝑢𝑒𝑠𝑡 𝑚𝑒 𝑏𝑜𝑡𝑠, 𝑠𝑖𝑚𝑝𝑙𝑦 𝑐𝑜𝑚𝑚𝑒𝑛𝑡 𝑖𝑡 𝑑𝑜𝑤𝑛 𝑏𝑒𝑙𝑜𝑤, 𝑓𝑢𝑟𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑟𝑚𝑜𝑟𝑒 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑐𝑎𝑛 𝑎𝑙𝑠𝑜 𝑝𝑢𝑡 𝑎𝑛 𝑒𝑥𝑎𝑐𝑡 𝑠𝑐𝑒𝑛𝑎𝑟𝑖𝑜 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑤𝑎𝑛𝑡, 𝑑𝑜𝑛'𝑡 𝑏𝑒 𝑠ℎ𝑦.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>[𝑁𝑂𝑁 𝑃𝑅𝐸𝐺𝑁𝐴𝑁𝑇 𝐴𝑈]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2571ef66-0739-46fa-a03e-ba822b1d8666_9fc40d57-c977-45a4-a4c1-bc150d2f02de.webp","creator":"gongyoo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":2111,"messages":22171,"created_at":"2025-01-01T06:55:52.157432+00:00"}